hair accessories</a> such as hair tinsel, or keep it flowing for a stunner effect. Making a comeback directly on the runway, this hairstyle is another all-time high-maintenance favourite, requiring a lot of care and patience. Going for the full retro look? Pair it with puffy side-swept <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/collections/fringe-clip-in-hair-extensions" target="_blank">bangs</a> for the ultimate 70s blowout.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-e573" data-pf-type="Section" id="shortandsweet" class="sc-jefHZX ePVSNw pf-140_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-ihINtW iHyUfe"><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-141_ pf-r" style="--s-xs:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bXdNzS hYBROi pf-142_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-jeraig eTNnJl pf-143_"><a data-link="inherit" href="#Index" target="_self"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eTwdGJ utmwk pf-145_">2022 Hairstyles Ideas: Short and Sweet&nbsp;</span></a></h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-146_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bXdNzS hYBROi pf-147_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-cRKLkh fMVExD pf-148_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/2022-hairstyles-ideas_-short-and-sweet-1641898938159_1200x.jpg?v=1641898939" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/2022-hairstyles-ideas_-short-and-sweet-1641898938159.jpg?v=1641898939 1536w" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-149_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bXdNzS hYBROi pf-150_"><p 